dct_creator_sm: Trinidad and Tobago. Lands & Surveys Department.
dct_description_sm: This map is Sheet 72 Edition 1-D.O.S. of the topographic map series E 804 Trinidad 1:25,000. It has been scanned, cropped to the map area, and georeferenced. Contour intervals are shown at 25 meters. Sheet History: Field survey by DOS & Lands & Surveys Division; Air photography -- Survair Mar 1969; Field revision by Lands & Surveys Dept 1975. Printed by Lands & Surveys Division in 1977. Published by Great Britain. Directorate of Overseas Surveys in 1970.
